data.description: Guests please use main gate on Veterans Memorial. Use code 6787 for entry. Step into luxury and elegance with this fully renovated 4-bedroom home featuring a master on the main level, full unfinished basement, brand new custom kitchen and 2-story ceilings throughout the main level. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's dream with Calcutta Quartz countertops, custom white cabinets, and new stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the view from the kitchen's spacious seating area onto the new back deck, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Another unique feature to this home is the screened in sunroom just off of the kitchen. The main level boasts new hardwood oak floors, while the upper level features plush new carpeting. The soaring 2-story ceiling in the main level creates a grand and spacious feel throughout. The home has been freshly painted both inside and out, with manicured landscaping and mulch completed in the last 2 weeks. Practical updates include a newer HVAC system (less than 6 years old), a recently replaced water heater (less than 4 years old), new plumbing, and duct work.   The full basement is ready for your customization, with plumbing already in place for a potential additional bedroom and bathroom. With ample space remaining, you can create your dream gym, media room, or entertainment space. Located in the high sought-after gated community community of Providence. The community features resort-style amenities including 2 swimming pools, 5 tennis courts, a dog park, and a fitness center, nature trail to the Chattahoochee River and sidewalks throughout.  This home offers both luxury and convenience. Easy commute to Hartsfield-Jackson, Buckhead, Midtown Atlanta, Smyrna, Truist Park and so much more! Don't let this one pass you by! Schedule a tour today!
